\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add breadcrumbs and mix <b>5 sec\/\/speed 3<b>."},{"content":"Stuff reserved tomatoes with prepared filling, and top each with two slices of mozzarella. Cover with reserved tops of tomatoes then place in Varoma dish."},{"content":"Place ½ tsp salt and stock cube in mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket, weigh rice in, then pour water over rice. Place covered Varoma into position and steam <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Set Varoma and simmering basket aside and keep rice and tomatoes warm. Empty mixing bowl, reserving steaming liquid."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Cashew and Basil Sauce"},{"content":"Place cashew nuts, 350 g tomato flesh and 150 g steaming liquid in mixing bowl then cook <b>4 min\/100°C\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add basil, lemon juice,  salt, ground pepper and sugar then blend <b>45 sec\/speed 4<b> <strong>-<\/strong> <strong>9, increasing speed gradually<\/strong>. Serve stuffed tomatoes and rice with sauce poured over."}],"basicInfo":["medium","45m","1h 30m","4 portions"]}